        :type: :ref:`Ethumb_Client_Thumb_FDO_Size` **writeonly**

        .. seealso:: :attr:`size`, :attr:`format`, :attr:`aspect`,
            :attr:`crop_align`, :attr:`category`, :attr:`dir_path`.

